Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要逃学…去远方的什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为被看见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么好放在心上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人都没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为悠你准备时故意磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长她眼睛通红诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想肯定都有些内情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日野君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心吧  那件事我不会告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…我觉得那样做很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个人  这么做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直喜欢春日野君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为你是个温柔  认真又出色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会和你说话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隐隐约约有些猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我希望是自己猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们…一直以来都是分开的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阔别许久回到我身边的穹  已经不是我所认识的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我从没见过的  一个纤弱柔美的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我真的…心跳不已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生过许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每都会让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那家伙很不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也因此  被她所依靠的时候更加让我怦然心动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想去守护她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是我妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她是我妹妹…不能跨出那一步…我总是这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是在两年后的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有了一段别的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想把它变成一段真正的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总是不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我却依然想把它硬撑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果伤害了奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是不太顺利呢  真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个人  这么做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我希望是自己猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭做好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？你怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实一点都没有改变呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎么糟蹋我的身体都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要悠你想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:07:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…不是这样的  不是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是结束吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是接吻…还是更亲昵的举动…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是兄妹啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在说这些？为什么是兄妹就不能接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不许性爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那个…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为不会被别人接受？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情我一点都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要和悠在一起就好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道还有其它很多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但全部都无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么  就算是悠的小孩我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实没你想得那么简单！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那万一有了就堕掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得那么轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说那些话？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经讨厌我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔发来短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:52.07,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我和真里子都在考虑让你们能\N过上安心的生活。只要你们方便\N的话，两个人分别住到我和真里\N子这边来怎么样。我和真里子一\N直都承蒙大哥照顾，所以我想我\N们也有将你们抚养成人的义务。\N具体等我回国之后直接见面谈吧。\N你和穹两个人都好好考虑一下。）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔他们要回日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和旭川阿姨已经谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们其实没多少储蓄…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢  这又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他们一个人可以收养我们中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们分开吧  这样才会更幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  穹你在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:46.43,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我虽然是悠的妹妹\N却想和悠接吻…\N想和悠连结在一起…\N但是这好像给悠添麻烦了呢…\N对不起…）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小悠  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹她…她不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以确定  她应该没有乘电车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她可能去别人家了  但哪里都没有人影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有哪些有可能的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的活动范围应该不会很大…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在音乐教室里我没和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹她和我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这样就扯平了」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夏天  小穹她好像看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穹她是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你还想和她分开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说正因为如此  你才要和她分开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在寻找答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去亮平家什么的看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你  奈绪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我家后面的湖从头开始吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于我们叉依姬神社内社的湖泊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说是万物起源
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比淤能碁吕岛更早存在  乃人类诞生之地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去那儿的话人就可以转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生就能从头开始了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  穹  没能救你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  也许这是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让两人一同前往只有两个人的遥远世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为再也不会睁开眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕  对于两人的前途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟会有什么等待着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我依然不知道该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  两个人一起寻找好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找能好好珍惜这份心意的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不计较他人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在意自己会多痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想找到最能让穹得到幸福的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你  穹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得这些成员凑在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉挺怀念的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感觉是他们把我们凑到了一块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发短信过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次之后音讯全无
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚离开机场准备坐巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再换乘几次当地的长途汽车和地区短线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.49,0:19:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概三天后到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到受过父母照顾的一个家具商的镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是天方夜谭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身两人去外国居住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂  这样真的能幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  对小悠来说  真正的挑战还在后头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就我而言  却不能断言小悠是错误的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  爱上一个人的感情是无法抑止的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望他们能得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光有感情就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感情就能为所欲为的话  我也有很多想做的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沾到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎饼干  在嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从伊福部小姐那里知道了来龙去脉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也问过家里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我必须得来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:24.72,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(313,305)}初佳与悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我比你小又不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没工作也挣不了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业后我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请永远留在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了来这里的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了  我停止的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:23:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.07,0:24:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出洋相了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是初佳的风格
